<p></p><p><section class="article135" data-role="outer" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">3月21日，江西软件职业技术大学校党委书记、督导专员江延湖在学术报告厅为学子们带来了一堂别开生面的“开学第一课”。他以“努力成为可堪大用、能担重任的时代新人”为主题，深入浅出地传达了习近平总书记考察江西时的重要讲话精神，引发了同学们的深思与共鸣。<br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-03-24%2013%3A44%3A44IMG_0043.jpg?Expires=2026619084&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=olUSeO2xeDJJx1aYHe9h2pI1EQA%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">江延湖首先引导同学们深入理解习近平总书记考察江西的重要意义。他强调，作为新时代的青年学子，应当充分认识习近平总书记考察江西的重要意义，并深刻领会总书记对江西工作的肯定与对江西发展的殷切期望。他又通过详细解读省委常委会（扩大）会议和全省领导干部会议的相关内容，他使同学们对总书记的重要讲话精神有了更加全面和深刻的认识。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">随后，江延湖以“物华天宝，‘四色’江西”为题，向同学们展示了江西丰富多彩的文化底蕴。他提出，新时代的江西以“红色”革命传统为底色，“绿色”生态发展为特色，“古色”文化传承为亮色,“金色”经济发展为成色，形成了独具特色的“四色”江西。他特别强调了“金色”江西的重要性，鼓励同学们为身为江西人而自豪，为建设江西而不懈奋斗。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">在课程的最后部分，江延湖聚焦于“时代有需，青年有为”的主题。他结合习近平总书记在二十大上的伟大号召，号召同学们要有理想、敢担当、能吃苦、肯奋斗，争做新时代好青年。他提出，新时代青年应做信仰如磐的理想青年、做勇挑大梁的担当青年、做愈挫愈勇的吃苦青年、做脚踏实地的奋斗青年。他谈到同学们应当珍惜时光，小憩可以，切勿荒废；要锤炼意志，也当强身健体；学好自己专业知识，实践增才干；紧跟时代潮流，勿纸上谈兵。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-03-24%2013%3A46%3A08IMG_0022.jpg?Expires=2026619169&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=QNKhvaUS3%2BpHh1etPbdJZ5qsoIM%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px; color: black !important;">课后，同学们深深感觉自己不仅更加深入学习了习近平总书记考察江西的重要讲话精神，还深刻领会了江西“四色”文化的独特魅力。大家纷纷表示，将牢记嘱托，珍惜时光，锤炼意志，努力成为可堪大用、能担重任的时代新人，为实现中国现代化建设和江西现代化建设贡献青春力量。</span></p></section></p><p></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-align: center; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px;">学校地址：江西省南昌市先锋创客小镇 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;邮编：330041</span></p><p><br/></p>